    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "AD 278 - Two smiling passengers relax and enjoy it as cocktails are served\nin the spacious lounge aft of the main cabin of a Pan American World Airways\n\"Super-6\" Clipper. The great Clipper, luxury version of Pan American's famous\nlow-cost \"Rainbow\" Clipper, carries passengers, cargo, and mail high over the\ntlantic between the Eastern and Western hemispheres at an average speed of\nfive-miles-a-minute."
    ],
